{"tid":338901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（船P溺斃）同行人稱死者抽筋狂抓身邊人 最終都係沉","createTime":"2017-07-28T14:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T16:00:33.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e212c6533b0c0a1f34ce7359aa481c961501cc56","tid":338901,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T14:46:08.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=i4O2m5rimADd5DDgBaY7RwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=a7a39902\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】人稱「阿龍」的19歲青年黃子龍，今午與友人到西貢大蛇灣遊船河，疑玩瀡滑梯時遇溺，約1個半小時後由消防蛙人救起送院，惜返魂乏術。據遊艇東主盧先生（34歲）表示，今日租船的為一班青年男女，他們一行17人，早上在西貢碼頭出發，傍晚6時回航。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當時盧將遊艇停泊大蛇灣，並在船尾打開瀡滑梯讓船上人士玩耍。盧事後向目擊者了解，得悉阿龍懂游泳，當時在船邊遇溺，不斷掙扎大嗌「抽筋，救命！」慌亂間用手抓住身邊一名友人當水泡借力，詎料卻將對方扯落水底，他形容：「嗰個比佢（阿龍）撳咗落水，飲水都飲到飽晒！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n附近同行友人見狀，即時上前營救，及時將被按落水下的友人救起拉回船上，但阿龍卻迅速沒頂沉落水底，盧指出：「（阿龍）2秒唔夠已經沉咗落去。」船上友人立即報警，並嘗試落水拯救，惜遍尋不獲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n獲救友人休息後無礙，但船上一片愁雲慘霧，非常擔心阿龍安危，惜最終傳來噩耗。盧表示，船上有提供浮條及救生衣等設備，當時部分人落水時有使用，至於遇溺2人有否使用則不太清楚，對於發生意外感到難過。<br />\n---<br />\n好似好恐怖"},{"pid":"8be4bd2f6ba69f6d7d942023db35bab860fe3996","tid":338901,"uid":65234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T14:51:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n盧指出：「（阿龍）2秒唔夠已經沉咗落去。」<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n屌 係真唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c161f3a58c2f16337cfe244dbd7c9ec90f4cda1","tid":338901,"uid":94457,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T14:52:47.000Z","msg":"正常抽筋都唔會咁快沉<br />\n唔通下面有野拉住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9bdd9cb68cf6686491a8b130f139b7defbe3d50","tid":338901,"uid":103421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T14:54:26.000Z","msg":"替身"},{"pid":"d4416216996f506556bee8235a03a09c8ae94a99","tid":338901,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T14:57:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f71accad9c8c1387dd9f6da219d6e4c7c4bcf69","tid":338901,"uid":16270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T14:59:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常抽筋都唔會咁快沉<br />\n唔通下面有野拉住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n爭扎係沉得快, 你睇過乜野正常 唔會咁快沉"},{"pid":"e2efb9a9bb1eeb9a35efe5608022a71796bb2260","tid":338901,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:12:47.000Z","msg":"izombie<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1ac92c720a2b7844a682e198e8fd7a1cdcb457","tid":338901,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:43:29.000Z","msg":"好明顯比人拉落去果個落水後係咁打踢佢啦<br />\n正常都會無端端拉埋落水"},{"pid":"2e7bd1e740732ed4f17c46a283e94f4996f6e859","tid":338901,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:47:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1116323df2b97c5295cf84f4203767f39983cbd","tid":338901,"uid":110761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:53:22.000Z","msg":"被人拉果個可能自然反應<br />\n一腳踢左佢落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f094f40682b5193bfa8ccb105203f9e00649a8bf","tid":338901,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T16:00:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>被人拉果個可能自然反應<br />\n一腳踢左佢落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會變誤殺<br />\n正常都會用惡魔風腳連環踢佢"}]}